      <abstract>
        <p>Correction of August 14 headline about Institute on the Arts and Civic Dialogue, performing program at Harvard founded by playwright Anna Deavere Smith</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>A headline last Monday about the Institute on the Arts and Civic Dialogue, a performing program at Harvard founded by the playwright Anna Deavere Smith, referred imprecisely to its end. It has closed, at least for now, because its three-year grant will expire this year, not because its offerings did not rally audiences.</p>
      </block>
